This is a text adventure based on a high school experience. There are many ways to die, and only a few ways to win.
Manage your stress carefully, and complete encounters using your trusty items.
IN THIS GAME:
Find powerful items, from The Crucible to the powers of god
Die because you used said items wrong
Die repeatedly thanks to the Save function
Escape the terror that is high school

Testing Credits to Massimo and Kathryn
Aesthetic Idea Credit to Giovanna

Enjoy the game, don't get discouraged, and try not to go insane.
